<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<bibRefCitation author="Habu, A" journalOrPublisher="Kontyu" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="257 - 259" refId="B13" refString="Habu, A, 1959. One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Kontyu 27: 257 - 259" title="One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae)." volume="27" year="1959">Habu (1959)</bibRefCitation>
describes 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai" subGenus="Peryphus">Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai</taxonomicName>
from Hokkaido, Japan, reporting that the species is closely related to 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus) amurense subsp. trajectum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="amurense" subGenus="Peryphus" subSpecies="trajectum">Bembidion (Peryphus) amurense trajectum</taxonomicName>
Netolitzky, 1939 (currently listed in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
). Later, the species was listed in 
<bibRefCitation author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Apollo Books, Stenstrup" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B28" refString="Marggi, W, Huber, C, Mueller-Motzfeld, G, Hartmann, M, 2003. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242-273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Apollo Books, Stenstrup" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242 - 273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2003">Marggi et al. (2003)</bibRefCitation>
in two different positions, within the subgenus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Ocydromus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ocydromus">Bembidion Ocydromus</taxonomicName>
but with the incorrect spelling 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">umeayi</emphasis>
(sic!) and within 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;incertae sedis&quot; with the correct name &quot; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion umeyai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;. The same mistake, reported to us by our colleague Katsuyuki Terada (Hiroshima), also occurs in 
<bibRefCitation author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B29" refString="Marggi, W, Toledano, L, Neri, P, 2017. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294-342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Brill, Leiden" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294 - 342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2017">Marggi et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
. In 
<bibRefCitation author="Habu, A" journalOrPublisher="Kontyu" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="257 - 259" refId="B13" refString="Habu, A, 1959. One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Kontyu 27: 257 - 259" title="One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae)." volume="27" year="1959">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Habuâ€™s">Habu's</normalizedToken>
(1959)
</bibRefCitation>
original description and in 
<bibRefCitation author="Morita, S" journalOrPublisher="Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B31" refString="Morita, S, 2001. On Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai Habu: 293-296. Papers on Coleoptera in honor of Toshifumi Hozumi. The Coleopteran Fauna of Tokai District." title="On Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai Habu: 293 - 296. Papers on Coleoptera in honor of Toshifumi Hozumi. The Coleopteran Fauna of Tokai District." year="2001">Morita (2001)</bibRefCitation>
the illustration of the aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion umeyai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shows that the species belongs to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
